Package: RHRT
Type: Package
Title: Scans for PVCs and calculates HRT Parameters
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-02-11
Author: Valeria Blesius
Maintainer: Valeria Blesius <valeria.blesius@mni.thm.de>
Description: The package provides methods to scan interval data for PVCs
    (premature ventricular complexes). It filters the results on the basis of
    Schmidt's filter rules and calculates the HRT parameters TO (turbulence onset)
    and TS (turbulence slope) (see http://www.h-r-t.com). A plot method helps
    visualise HRT.
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    methods
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
